name: CountryCaller
0:
”Alexa, ask Country Caller what is the dialing code for Great Britain?”
”Which country has the dialing code 61?”
”How do I call Germany?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: country caller
des: Country caller is a simple utility which provides three things: 1) Lookup country codes for 200+ countries; 2) Reverse Lookup - supply the dialing code and the skill will tell you which country is calling; 3) Complete dialing instructions for country-to-country calls on mobile & landline.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
